OL,6,FCrossCountry Trains told the ASA the
OL,7,Fperiod leading up to the complainants
OL,8,Fseeing the ad ` September to November
OL,9,F2023 ` was marked by "exceptional
OL,10,Fdisruption" due to industrial action
OL,11,Fand four storms.
OL,13,FIt had planned to offer catering,
OL,14,Fincluding first-class food and drink,
OL,15,Fon between 70% and 78% of its Voyager
OL,16,Froutes, which operated on most of its
OL,17,Flong-distance services from September
OL,18,Fto November 2023, with slight
OL,19,Fvariations depending on the day of the
OL,20,Fweek.
